eakpoints: {\n       0: {\n         slidesPerView: 1,\n         spaceBetween: 20,\n       },\n       768: {\n         slidesPerView: 1,\n         spaceBetween: 30,\n       },\n       1024: {\n         slidesPerView: 2,\n         spaceBetween: 30,\n       },\n        \n     },\n     \n   });\n   \n</script>\n','Attorney section','','publish','closed','closed','','attorney-section','','','2023-05-24 10:01:05','2023-05-24 10:01:05','',0,'http://localhost:10035/?post_type=lc_section&amp;p=3796',0,'lc_section','',0),(3921,1,'2023-05-25 07:40:40','2023-05-25 07:40:40','<div class=\"container\">\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“The Walker Firm was most helpful for handling my personal injury case. They were honest, hardworking, down-to-Earth, and ethical. They were both instrumental and patient in working with a difficult third party on my behalf. They were consistent and thorough with communication. They were an advantageous advocate for my case and truly went above and beyond for my case. I am thankful that they have represented me.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- K. Daniels</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“I just wanted to take a few minutes to make you aware of 2 very awesome lawyers at the Walker Law Firm. I was very pleased with the performance, support professionalism and determination of both Jay Walker and his son C.J. Walker. Throughout my case, both lawyers were always very quick to respond, made themselves available during times that most would consider after hours and always patient in explaining the status and details/developments of my case. I might add that it will be very difficult to find another law firm who cares about their clients the way this firm does!\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- J. Foshee</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“I have worked with both Jay and C.J., and they each showed a high degree of professionalism and an understanding of law combined with a concern for their client. Recently, my family worked with C.J. regarding legal work and found him to be patient, a good listener, and considerate of the elderly, while at the same time, competent, skillful, and well informed of the law. I would highly recommend this law firm.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- W. Bell</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“If you are looking for a law firm with exceptional knowledge of the law and a great work ethic, I highly recommend THE WALKER FIRM. I have known Jay for many years and know him to be a great lawyer and humanitarian. Both Jay and C. J. have represented my family in legal maters. C. J. recently worked with us and I could not be more pleased with his efforts and the outcome. Consider THE WALKER FIRM the next time you need legal assistance.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- P. Tackett</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“C.J. Walker is great! He helped me in so many ways. He is very personable while doing everything he can to help you . Everyone was very nice and helpful. By him using his legal knowledge, I was relieved of a lot of stress and worry. I will certainly go to Mr. Walker again whenever I need some legal matters taken care of. Thank You C.J. Walker.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- P. Kincaid</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“Everyone was very nice ready to help me out with my situation. I am very appreciative for how they handled everything and kept me informed of what was going on the whole time. I highly recommend the Walker firm for any case you might need taken care of.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- J. Christensen</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“I hired C.J. Walker to represent me in a legal dispute, and not only did he win my case, but every aspect of his representation was outstanding. His preparation for court, including preparing me to testify, and his presentation of my case in court were exceptional. He asked thoughtful, probing questions during witness testimony that elicited the information the judge needed to rule in my favor. I spent a lot of time searching for the right lawyer, and I\'m absolutely certain hiring The Walker Firm was the right decision.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- M. Taylor</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“J.C. Walker and his firm are truly amazing. They care about their client and they work hard to make sure they do everything possible on each case. It\'s hard to put into words how extraordinary this firm is..\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Terri</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“The Walker Firm helped me with my criminal case and did an amazing job. CJ Walker is very professional, knowledgeable, and respectful and kept me informed during the whole process. I had a difficult case and CJ went above and beyond and kept me from doing any prison time. I can not thank him enough during this difficult time. I highly recommend this law firm. You will not be disappointed!!!\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Jay B.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“If you are looking for the best of the best then you’ve found it! Cj is outstanding. Me and my family HIGHLY RECOMMEND using The Walker Firm!!!\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Trevor B.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“Great guy, if I could rate him with 10 stars I would.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Jermaine L.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“Let me start by saying they deserve more than 5 stars. I used The Walker Firm in 2014 and 2015 and they were amazing! They were able to see me the same day when I reached out for help. Their staff is extremely helpful and the knowledgeable. I received the best possible outcome in both situations and that is a true testament to the hard work and dedications of the staff in The Walker Firm. Not only did they answer all of my questions but they were able to communicate with my wife and put her mind at ease; which might I add is not small task. Their assistance does not stop when your case is over as I have called for various questions and they were always available. I can not thank them enough for all of the help they gave me. They are and will always be my first call when or if I need anything.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Parise O.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“The Walker Family is the best! I am so thankful for the outcome of service. I could not imagine a better outcome on my case. I had the pleasure of working with CJ Walker and his service was impeccable! I loved the hospitality received when I visited the office. I highly recommend this office for representation!\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Adasia W.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“I just would like to thank Mr. Walker for being my lawyer the past three years he is a great stand up guy and has the knowledge to get the job done always. He is very attentive and doesn\'t stop until you get the ultimate results that you want to have or at least gets you close to it. This firm is definitely a firm I would recommend to anybody that is in a jam or either wanting just overall good representation. Thank you Walker firm for everything that you have done for me. I would not go to anyone else in the 478 radius because this firm is the one you would want to represent you.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Ashley M.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“The Walker Firm was most helpful for handling my personal injury case. They were honest, hardworking, down-to-Earth, and ethical. They were both instrumental and patient in working with a difficult third party on my behalf. They were consistent and thorough with communication. They were an advantageous advocate for my case and truly went above and beyond for my case. I am thankful that they have represented me.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Little J.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“The Walker Firm not only helped me when legal assistance was needed, but truly amazed me with how well they handled my personal legal matter. (I’ve worked with many attorney’s in my professional career and can tell you in general attorneys are extremely busy.) This office staff and Attorney C.J. Walker ALWAYS made me feel like they had time for me no matter how busy they were. Their wealth of legal knowledge and genuine care for their client’s well being is greatly appreciated. I highly recommend this firm.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Danielle G.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“The Walker Firm is absolutely amazing! Mr. Walker was extremely quick and responsive! He worked around the clock on my case and kept me informed throughout the process. Absolutely amazing would recommend to anyone!\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Beth B.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“The Walker Firm went above and beyond my expectations ; even going out of their way to help me find the right divorce attorney. The Walker Firm is very friendly and respectful to its clients. The Walker Firm is very straightforward and leaves no \"gray area\" within a client\'s case. The Walker Firm completely defends their clients whole heartedly and aggressively fights in the clients favor. The Walker Firm is an excellent choice for anyone acquiring a lawyer for a criminal case, personal injury, and civil suites . You will not be disappointed , I give The Walker Firm ☆☆☆☆☆☆☆☆☆☆ (10/10).\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Haley S.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“When it comes to matters regarding elderly family members it can, at times, be overwhelming. I have to say dealing with C.J. Walker has lifted a great burden from our family. He is kind, quick to respond, takes the time to thoroughly explain and seems to care for the well-being of our family. I would without a doubt highly recommend C.J. Walker to anyone. Angie Steed Kivett\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Whitney S.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“I recently had CJ Walker and his staff prepare some legal documents for my wife and I, they accommodated our short suspense. They were very professional and did an outstanding job, the fee was very reasonable. I would highly recommend the Walker Firm.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Sean D.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“I used Mr. H.J. walker in the past and was very satisfied, so when I required legal services again due to a collision, I went back. This time around I had the pleasure of dealing with Mr. C.J Walker and Ms. Brumfield. I was again very satisfied with the services provided. Through the entire process, they kept me informed of any developments as well as the current status of my case. End result was a very satisfied client. I would definitely use their services again should I have legal issues that require it and I would not hesitate to recommend them to friends or family.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Sunil C.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“The Walker Firm. CJ and Senior Walker are the real deal. If I could give them 10 stars I would. Thank you Walker Firm for everything you are and have done. When I went to the review. It was 4.9 and I see why now. Thanks again.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Christopher P.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“Everyone was very nice ready to help me out with my situation. I am very appreciative for how they handled everything and kept me informed of what was going on the whole time. I highly recommend the Walker firm for any case you might need taken care of.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- Justin C.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\r\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\r\n“I just wanted to say thank you to CJ Walker for going above and beyond for us. He is a very skilled, compassionate, patient, thorough and effective lawyer who I would put my trust in again if needed. Excellent outcome!!\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- karen G.</strong>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\"><a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/place/The+Walker+Firm/@32.5950857,-83.6657222,17z/data=!4m8!3m7!1s0x88f3e0