\">\n										<h5>Redemption Period Assistance</h5>\n										<p>The redemption period can make or break an investment. Our firm is equipped to step in should challenges arise involving homeowners, servicers, mortgage companies, and any other interested parties.<br></p>\n									</div>\n								</div>\n								<div class=\"flex-shrink-0\">\n									<img src=\"https://mdtaxsale.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Icon.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"rounded-circle wp-image-196\" alt=\"Redemption Period Assistance\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\">\n								</div>\n							</div>\n						</div>\n\n\n						<div class=\"swiper-slide lc-block\">\n							<div class=\"d-flex align-items-center\">\n								<div class=\"flex-grow-1 me-3 text-end\">\n									<div editable=\"rich\">\n										<h5>Negotiating on Your Behalf</h5>\n										<p>Our strong negotiation skills ensure that you are getting the most out of your investment. Once you choose to invest, we speak with external parties on your behalf so that any roadblocks that may come up along the way can be avoided.<br></p>\n									</div>\n								</div>\n								<div class=\"flex-shrink-0\">\n									<img src=\"https://mdtaxsale.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Icon.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"rounded-circle wp-image-196\" alt=\"Negotiating on Your Behalf\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\">\n								</div>\n							</div>\n						</div>\n\n\n						<div class=\"swiper-slide lc-block\">\n							<div class=\"d-flex align-items-center\">\n								<div class=\"flex-grow-1 me-3 text-end\">\n									<div editable=\"rich\">\n										<h5 data-spkac-font-size=\"20\">Management of Court Proceedings</h5>\n										<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">The skilled attorneys at LewisMcDaniels manage every part of the tax lien foreclosure process – from drafting the required documents and notices to the completion of all pleadings and motions.<br data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n									</div>\n								</div>\n								<div class=\"flex-shrink-0\">\n									<img src=\"https://mdtaxsale.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Icon.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"rounded-circle wp-image-196\" alt=\"Management of Court Proceedings\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\">\n								</div>\n							</div>\n						</div>\n\n\n						<div class=\"swiper-slide lc-block\">\n							<div class=\"d-flex align-items-center\">\n								<div class=\"flex-grow-1 me-3 text-end\">\n									<div editable=\"rich\">\n										<h5 data-spkac-font-size=\"20\">Maximizing ROI</h5>\n										<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Your return on investment is a vital part of the tax sales process. Our firm gives you the peace of mind you deserve by ensuring that your investment is worth it.<br data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n									</div>\n								</div>\n								<div class=\"flex-shrink-0\">\n									<img src=\"https://mdtaxsale.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Icon.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"rounded-circle wp-image-196\" alt=\"Maximizing ROI\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\">\n								</div>\n							</div>\n						</div>\n\n\n						<div class=\"swiper-slide lc-block\">\n							<div class=\"d-flex align-items-center\">\n								<div class=\"flex-grow-1 me-3 text-end\">\n									<div editable=\"rich\">\n										<h5 data-spkac-font-size=\"20\">Mitigation of Tax Sale Title Issues</h5>\n										<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Whatever issues may arise along the way, our competent team at LewisMcDaniels is here to come up with practical solutions so that we can successfully close on your investment.<br data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n									</div>\n								</div>\n								<div class=\"flex-shrink-0\">\n									<img src=\"https://mdtaxsale.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Icon.png\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"rounded-circle wp-image-196\" alt=\"Mitigation of Tax Sale Title Issues\" width=\"80\" height=\"80\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"