			</div>\n\n								<p>Family Law: As the name implies, family law deals with legal issues pertaining to family matters. These are often extremely high-stakes, highly sensitive, and highly personal cases that require an attorney with high emotional intelligence in addition to a strong legal mind. Attorney Coolidge is exactly that type of attorney, and prides herself on her client-focused, strategy-based approach to family law cases. </p>\n								<p></p>\n								<p> </p>\n								<p>Attorney Coolidge offers representation in virtually all family law matters, including:</p>\n								<p></p>\n								<ul>\n									<li>Divorce and Marriage Dissolution<br></li>\n									<li>Paternity Actions&nbsp;<br></li>\n									<li>Time Sharing and Visitation<br></li>\n									<li>Prenuptial Agreements<br></li>\n									<li>Child Support&nbsp;<br></li>\n									<li>Restraining Orders&nbsp;<br></li>\n									<li>Legal Separation&nbsp;<br></li>\n									<li>Child Custody&nbsp;<br></li>\n									<li>Alimony/Spousal Support<br></li>\n									<li>Postnuptial Agreements<br></li>\n									<li>Domestic Violence&nbsp;<br></li>\n									<li>Parenting Agreements and Modification of Parenting Agreements</li>\n								</ul>\n								<p></p>\n								<p></p>\n								<p></p>\n							</div>\n							<div editable=\"rich\" class=\"tab-pane fade\" id=\"tab2\" role=\"tabpanel\" aria-labelledby=\"home-tab2\">\n								<div class=\"right-img\">\n									<img class=\"img-fluid wp-image-4476\" src=\"https://coolidgelaw.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Tab-Image.jpg\" width=\"573\" height=\"344\" srcset=\"https://coolidgelaw.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Tab-Image.jpg 573w, https://coolidgelaw.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Tab-Image-300x180.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" alt=\"\">\n								</div>\n								<p>\n									It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout. T