-md-12\">\n				<div class=\"content-sec\">\n					<img class=\"img-fluid wp-image-4499\" src=\"https://coolidgelaw.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Image.jpg\" width=\"573\" height=\"368\" srcset=\"https://coolidgelaw.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Image.jpg 573w, https://coolidgelaw.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Image-300x193.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 573px) 100vw, 573px\" alt=\"\">\n				</div>\n				<div class=\"\">\n					<div editable=\"rich\">\n						<p>Attorney Camille Coolidge is the lead attorney at the Coolidge Law Group, a multi-service law firm in Ft. Lauderdale, Florida. She is also the founder, hanging the Coolidge Law Group shingle in 2005. </p>\n						<p></p>\n						<p> </p>\n						<p>With over 18 years of legal experience, Attorney Coolidge is primarily focused on family law and helping families through the legal process, in addition to a suite of other legal services that may be of use to families and individuals. </p>\n						<p> </p>\n						<p>A south Florida native and the proud daughter of a decorated Air Force Captain, Attorney Coolidge has her roots firmly planted in Florida soil and grew up imbued with the values of hard work and always treating others with respect. </p>\n						<p> </p>\n						<p>Before graduating from the Nova Southeastern University School of Law, Attorney Coolidge had a first career as an entrepreneur, running a small business newspaper to promote small business and community interests in Murphy, North Carolina.</p>\n						<p>However, her passion has always been families—including her own. With her husband, former Ft. Lauderdale Police Detective Mark Shotwell, Camille has raised her sister’s children, Clayton and Lily, since infancy. Their successful lives as independent adults today is one of her greatest sources of pride and joy. </p>\n						<p></p>\n						<p> </p>\n						<p>The process of raising a non-conventional or blended family has also given Attorney Coolidge unique insight into the many ways a family can be made, as well as the many complications of navigating the legal system when it comes to family matters. If you are facing a family law case, Attorney Coolidge is uniquely qualified to empathize with your struggle and advocate on your behalf, making the process as pain-free as possible. </p>\n						<p> </p>\n						<p>Attorney Coolidge has been recognized by and included among the Top Attorneys of North America, a New York based publication distinguishing leading, successful attorneys around the country.</p>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</section>\n<section>\n	<div class=\"\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-6 px-0\">\n				<div class=\"lc-block bg-dark text-white\">\n					<div class=\"home_office_direction\">\n						<div editable=\"rich\">\n							<h2 class=\"text-white text-start\">How To Find Us?<br></h2>\n							<p>We work as a single unified team to give our clients the highest quality advice possible and solve the situations with great results. </p>\n							<br>\n							<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"text-secondary\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n								<path d=\"M8 16s6-5.686 6-10A6 6 0 0 0 2 6c0 4.314 6 10 6 10zm0-7a3 3 0 1 1 0-6 3 3 0 0 1 0 6z\"></path>\n							</svg>\n							<p class=\"\"><strong class=\"text-secondary\">Address:</strong> 110 SE 6th Street, Suite 1700, Fort Lauderdale, FL 33301 </p>\n							<hr>\n							<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"1em\" height=\"1em\" fill=\"currentColor\" class=\"text-secondary\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\">\n								<path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M1.885.511a1.745 1.745 0 0 1 2.61.163L6.29 2.98c.329.423.445.974.315 1.494l-.547 2.19a.678.678 0 0 0 .178.643l2.457 2.457a.678.678 0 0 0 .644.178l2.189-.547a1.745 1.745 0 0 1 1.494.315l2.306 1.794c.829.645.905 1.87.163 2.611l-1.034 1.034c-.74.74-1.846 1.065-2.877.702a18.634 18.634 0 0 1-7.01-4.42 18.634 18.634 0 0 1-4.42-7.009c-.362-1.03-