e=\"rich\">\n						<h2> You Deserve The <br> Best. You’re In The <br> Right Place.</h2>\n						<hr>\n						<p>I founded this practice using the most up-to-date technology and trailblazing defense strategies to get justice for the people of Central Florida. My reputation for candor and focus is the cornerstone of my practice. I’ll take charge of your case, walk you through the process with integrity, and get the outcome you deserve.<br></p>\n						<p><a href=\"#\" class=\"btn btn-primary btnall deserve-btn\">My Experience And Education</a><br></p>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"bg-light pt-5 pb-5\">\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n				<div class=\"lc-block\">\n					<div editable=\"rich\">\n						<h2 class=\"text-center\">Schedule A Consultation</h2>\n						<p class=\"text-center\">You need an experienced attorney who will listen, understand, and take a cutting-edge approach to your defense to get you the best result. Put expertise and innovation to work for YOU.<br></p>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n				<div class=\"lc-block\">\n					<div lc-helper=\"shortcode\" class=\"live-shortcode\">[cForm]</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</section>\n','Home','','inherit','closed','closed','','4650-revision-v1','','','2023-06-19 04:38:16','2023-06-19 04:38:16','',4650,'http://localhost:10065/?p=4772',0,'revision','',0),(4773,1,'2023-06-19 04:39:00','2023-06-19 04:39:00','\n<section>\n	<div lc-helper=\"shortcode\" class=\"live-shortcode\">[lc_get_post post_type=\"lc_section\" slug=\"banner-9\"]</div>\n</section>\n<section>\n	<div lc-helper=\"shortcode\" class=\"live-shortcode\">[lc_get_post post_type=\"lc_section\" slug=\"video-section\"]</div>\n</section>\n<section>\n	<div lc-helper=\"shortcode\" class=\"live-shortcode\">[lc_get_post post_type=\"lc_section\" slug=\"case-results\"]</div>\n</section>\n<section>\n	<div lc-helper=\"shortcode\" class=\"live-shortcode\">[lc_get_post post_type=\"lc_section\" slug=\"practice-areas-2-2\"]</div>\n</section>\n<section>\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n				<div class=\"lc-block\">\n					<div editable=\"rich\">\n						<h2 class=\"text-center text-uppercase\" data-spkac-font-size=\"32\">why The walker firm?<img src=\"https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/border.png\" width=\"11\" height=\"54\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\" alt=\"Line\" class=\"wp-image-4857 mx-auto d-block\" data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></h2>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"pt-4 pb-xl-6 pb-4\">\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n				<div class=\"lc-block\">\n					<div editable=\"rich\">\n						<div class=\"text-center float-md-start pe-md-3\">\n							<img class=\"img-fluid wp-image-4905 pb-3\" src=\"https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/img-6.png\" width=\"570\" height=\"331\" srcset=\"https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/img-6.png 570w, https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/img-6-300x174.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 570px) 100vw, 570px\" alt=\"Our Reputation - Personal Injury &amp;  Criminal Defense Attorney - Warner Robins, GA\">\n						</div>\n						<p>Choosing a law firm can be overwhelming, particularly when legal issues already burden you. But The Walker Firm offers distinct advantages.<br></p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"> </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Our deep roots in Warner Robins provide us with a unique edge in comprehending local laws and traversing the legal terrain. We\'re more than your lawyers—we\'re your neighbors, familiar with the courts, judges, and prosecutors. We can leverage this knowledge to your benefit. </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Our commitment to our clients sets us apart. We realize that behind every case is a person in need. We treat you with respect and compassion, keeping you informed throughout your case and always making ourselves available to answer your questions. </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"><strong data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Why Should I Choose A Local Warner Robins Firm Instead Of A More Prominent National Firm? </strong></p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Being a local firm, we have an intimate understanding of the unique legal contours of Warner Robins and Georgia law. Our ties with local courts, judges, and prosecutors could be a boon to your case. Plus, we offer a personalized service often missing at larger firms. </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"><strong data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">How does The Walker Firm approach auto accident cases? </strong></p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Our approach begins with a comprehensive investigation of the incident. We compile and scrutinize all the necessary evidence in collaboration with accident reconstruction experts and medical professionals. To establish liability, we meticulously gather police reports, witness statements, medical records, and any other pertinent documentation. </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"> </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Having built a strong case, we tackle complex negotiations with insurance companies for you. We strive to secure fair compensation for your injuries, property damage, lost wages, and other associated losses. Our vast experience and negotiation prowess counter lowball settlement offers to ensure you\'re adequately compensated. </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"> </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">We ensure you\'re updated and informed throughout the process so you understand your rights and options. </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"><strong data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">What types of criminal law offenses can The Walker Firm help with? </strong></p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">We provide proficient representation across a broad array of criminal law offenses, such as: </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"> </p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n						<ul data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">\n							<li data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Alcohol-related cases </li>\n							<li data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Assault &amp; Battery </li>\n							<li data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Burglary, Theft, and Criminal Fraud </li>\n							<li data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Domestic Violence </li>\n							<li data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Drug Crimes </li>\n							<li data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Felonies and Misdemeanors </li>\n							<li data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Homicide </li>\n							<li data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Traffic Violations </li>\n							<li data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Weapons Charges </li>\n						</ul>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n						<p></p>\n					</div>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n</section>\n<section style=\"background:url(https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bg-3.jpg)  center / cover no-repeat;\" class=\"wp-image-4912 tstimonial-sec pt-xl-7 pb-xl-8 pt-5 pb-5\">\n	<div class=\"container\">\n		<div class=\"row\">\n			<div class=\"col-md-12\">\n				<div class=\"lc-block\">\n					<div editable=\"rich\">\n						<h2 class=\"text-center text-white text-uppercase\">Client Testimonials</h2>\n						<img src=\"https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/border.png\" class=\"wp-image-4857 mx-auto d-block\" width=\"11\" height=\"54\" srcset=\"\" sizes=\"\" alt=\"Line\">\n						<p class=\"text-white text-center\">“The Walker Firm goes above and beyond consistently to make sure you’re taken care of. You can trust this team has your best interest in mind, I promise you!”<br></p>\n						<h5 class=\"text-center text-white\">- Jade M.</h5>\n						<p><a href=\"/client-testimonials/\" 