ible results.\n<h4>How Can I Make A Difference For You?</h4>\nI make a difference by advocating passionately for my clients. My deep understanding of the laws in the areas I practice, combined with my caring demeanor and readiness to be aggressive when necessary, positions me to treat each client\'s case as if they were my own family.\n<h4>A Track Record That Speaks For Itself</h4>\nOver 43 years of practice, I\'ve been successful in securing proper compensation for injured clients and favorable outcomes in criminal cases.\n<h4>Reach Out Today</h4>\nIf you or a loved one has been injured or is facing criminal charges, don\'t hesitate to reach out at (478) 923-4152. With an approach that is aggressive, effective, and caring, my law firm is ready to treat you like family and do everything in our power to secure the best possible outcome for you.','About The Attorney','','inherit','closed','closed','','5035-autosave-v1','','','2023-06-23 07:51:40','2023-06-23 07:51:40','',5035,'https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/?p=5111',0,'revision','',0),(5112,1,'2023-06-22 10:30:31','2023-06-22 10:30:31','<div class=\"container\">\n\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n“The Walker Firm was most helpful for handling my personal injury case. They were honest, hardworking, down-to-Earth, and ethical. They were both instrumental and patient in working with a difficult third party on my behalf. They were consistent and thorough with communication. They were an advantageous advocate for my case and truly went above and beyond for my case. I am thankful that they have represented me.\"<strong class=\"text-end d-block\">- K. Daniels</strong>\n\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"spk-testimonial-wrap rounded mb-3 py-3 px-3\">\n<div class=\"clearfix\"></div>\n“I just wanted to take a few minutes to make you aware of 2 very awesome lawyers at the Walker Law Firm. I was very pleased with the performance, support professionalism and determination of b