 we\'re more than just a collective of attorneys—we\'re a dynamic team of problem solvers. Our legal prowess spans multiple fields, including personal injury law, criminal defense, auto accidents, DUI cases, and traffic law, each with its unique challenges and complexities. </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"> </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">When it comes to personal injury, our mission is clear: to secure fair compensation for those wronged by others\' negligence. We serve as your unwavering advocates, standing up to insurance companies intent on downplaying your suffering and loss. </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"> </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">Facing criminal charges? Our defense lawyers are on hand to protect your rights and ensure you\'re treated justly. By meticulously dissecting the prosecution\'s case, we can identify any weaknesses, challenging them while affirming your innocence. </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"> </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">In the wake of auto accidents, our seasoned attorneys guide you through the aftermath, tackling insurance claims and lawsuits so that you can focus on recuperating. </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"> </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">With DUI cases, the stakes are high. Our DUI lawyers provide lucid, no-nonsense advice, guiding you through the legal maze while striving for the optimal outcome. </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"> </p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\">For those facing traffic violations, be it a minor speeding ticket or a serious offense, our traffic lawyers will make sure you comprehend your options and possible penalties while advocating for a beneficial resolution. </p>\n					<h4 data-spkac-font-size=\"24\">\n						<p data-spkac-font-size=\"24\"></p>\n					</h4>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n					<p data-spkac-font-size=\"16\"></p>\n				</div>\n			</div>\n		</div>\n	</div>\n	<style>\n		/*------------------video section----------*/\n.video-right{\n    float: right;\n    width: 50%;\n    margin-left: 15px;\n}\n		@media (max-width: 900px) {\n		 .video-right{\n        float: none;\n    width: 100%;\n    margin: 0 0 15px;\n    }\n		}\n	</style>\n</section>\n','Video section - Copy','','trash','closed','closed','','__trashed','','','2023-06-26 11:31:07','2023-06-26 11:31:07','',0,'https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/?post_type=lc_section&#038;p=5176',0,'lc_section','',0),(5177,1,'2023-06-26 12:06:33','2023-06-26 12:06:33','<section class=\"banner-background\" style=\"background:url(https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/bg-1.jpg)  center / cover no-repeat;\">\r\n	<div class=\"container\">\r\n		<div class=\"banner-top\">\r\n			<div class=\"banner-left\">\r\n				<div class=\"lc-block\">\r\n\r\n					<a href=\"/attorney-profile/charles-walker/\">\r\n						<img class=\"img-fluid wp-image-5062  d-lg-none d-block\" src=\"https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Responisve-Image.png\" width=\"299\" height=\"323\" srcset=\"https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Responisve-Image.png 299w, https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Responisve-Image-278x300.png 278w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 299px) 100vw, 299px\" alt=\"\">\r\n						<img class=\"img-fluid wp-image-4778  d-lg-block d-none\" src=\"https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Attorney-pic.png\" width=\"539\" height=\"754\" srcset=\"https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Attorney-pic.png 539w, https://thewalkerfirm.wpengine.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/06/Attorney-pic-214x300.png 214w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 539px) 100vw, 539px\" alt=\"Experienced Georgia Personal Injury &amp;  Criminal Defense Attorney - Charles Walker, Esq.\">\r\n					</a>\r\n				</div>\r\n			</div>\r\n			<div cl